<para style="q1">

<verse number="30" style="v" />If his children forsake my law</para>

<para style="q1">and disobey my decrees,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="31" style="v" />if they break my rules</para>

<para style="q1">and do not keep my commands,</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="32" style="v" />then will I punish their rebellion with a rod</para>

<para style="q1">and their iniquity with blows.</para>
